# Rust build artifacts
/target

# Build-time oracle generator virtualenv (Plan 03). NOT the fixtures, which are
# committed frozen (D-11/D-12) — `crates/cb-oracle/fixtures/` is intentionally
# tracked and must never be ignored.
crates/cb-oracle/generator/.venv/

# CatBoost training-log output emitted by the generator (NOT a fixture). The
# gen_fixtures.py training run writes a catboost_info/ dir of TSV/event logs we
# never consume — keep it out of git. The generator may emit this dir relative
# to either its own cwd or the cb-oracle crate root, so ignore both.
crates/cb-oracle/generator/catboost_info/
crates/cb-oracle/catboost_info/
